# Sandbox Sync Rule

To ensure consistent security boundaries, always keep `.cursor/sandbox.json` in sync with the `sandbox` section of `.claude/settings.json`.

## Guidelines

- If `sandbox.network.allowedDomains` is updated in `.claude/settings.json`, update `networkPolicy.allow` in `.cursor/sandbox.json`.
- Ensure `.cursor/sandbox.json` remains the source of truth for Cursor Agent sessions.
